The band has released 4 singles before this album&#039;s release,
Parallel Worlds, Jessica, The White One Is Evil and Still Figuring Out,

the course of 2007, however Alex Davies, the front man, confirmed on a
BBC Radio 1 interview that the album would be released on the 21st April 2008.
